metadata.name: Reiteration Circle
metadata.description:
Reiteration Circle

Reiteration, a series based on the theme of repetition, rotation and juxtaposition. The "Reiteration Circle" is the master image behind the whole series with a size of 9987 x 9987 px. Zig thousands of lines form this circle in a chaotic yet sorted and structured way. Zooming into the image, this fascinating structure becomes much more recognizable. White lines on black background, a homage to the simplicity of multiplicity.
